    "bug-dist-zilla-pluginbundle-idoperel at rt.cpan.org", or through the
    web interface at
    <http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/ReportBug.html?Queue=Dist-Zilla-PluginBundle-
    IDOPEREL>. I will be notified, and then you'll automatically be notified
    of progress on your bug as I make changes.

